### JSON 버전 그룹 등록

POST http://localhost:3000/api/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "운동실허",
  "description": "하지만 해야겠지?",
  "photoUrl": "https://picsum.photos/200/300",
  "goalRep": 0,
  "discordWebhookUrl": "https://discord.com/api/webhooks/123/abc",
  "discordInviteUrl": "https://discord.gg/eternalreturn",
  "tags": [
    "이터널 리턴", "운동"
  ],
  "ownerNickname": "못바",
  "ownerPassword": "1234"
}

### JSON 버전 그룹 등록 2

POST http://localhost:3000/api/groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "스쿼트100",
  "description": "하루 100개 도전!",
  "photoUrl": "https://picsum.photos/200/200",
  "goalRep": 100,
  "discordWebhookUrl": "https://discord.com/api/webhooks/abc/xyz",
  "discordInviteUrl": "https://discord.gg/abcd",
  "tags": ["운동", "스쿼트"],
  "ownerNickname": "재성",
  "ownerPassword": "1234"
}

### 그룹 참여

POST http://localhost:3000/api/participants/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "영욱",
  "password": "1234"
}

### 그룹 참여 취소

